WEBVTT

01:19.800 --> 01:22.320
Rob, you're standing on my feet.

01:22.400 --> 01:25.840
I'm not standing on your feet.
You're standing on my feet.

01:28.120 --> 01:30.560
You've done an incredible job, Jo.

01:32.840 --> 01:34.480
