03:47.240 --> 03:50.200
Will you get me a nightgown
from home, please?

03:50.280 --> 03:53.400
I can't spend another night
with polyester on.

03:53.480 --> 03:55.280
Yeah. Is there
anything else you need?

03:56.720 --> 04:00.480
Maybe some clothes for the morning
and a washbag, please.

04:00.560 --> 04:02.040
Sorry if I was over the top.

04:02.120 --> 04:04.920
Somebody's gotta stick up for you
with these doctors.

04:06.520 --> 04:07.720
I'll see you later.

04:43.000 --> 04:46.720
- Mrs. Harding? Can I come in?
- Just a minute.

04:49.920 --> 04:54.680
- I am so sorry. I have to go.
- This really isn't a good idea.

04:55.800 --> 04:57.600
So, you can't stop me?

04:59.080 --> 05:01.800
That's right, isn't it?
You can't stop me.

05:08.120 --> 05:09.880
<i>Trust your instincts, Jo.</i>

05:11.800 --> 05:14.280
<i>That's the only way
you'll find out what happened.</i>

05:32.720 --> 05:33.680
Hello?

05:34.560 --> 05:36.240
This is Jo.

05:37.120 --> 05:42.360
I'd really like to talk to you,
and I need a place to stay tonight.

05:42.440 --> 05:43.960
Can you please call me back?

05:45.560 --> 05:46.560
Thank you.

05:55.240 --> 05:56.800
<i>Trust your instincts.</i>

06:17.360 --> 06:18.360
Mum?

06:20.840 --> 06:21.960
Jo...

06:27.240 --> 06:28.520
You'd better come in.

07:06.000 --> 07:08.200
I don't remember much from last year.

07:09.720 --> 07:12.280
