with an imaginary friend.

09:03.360 --> 09:04.520
Come on, Jo.

09:06.360 --> 09:08.080
Yes, I've seen him a bit stressed.

09:08.160 --> 09:10.600
The odd stapler's
taken one for the team, but...

09:11.200 --> 09:16.560
are you suggesting that he pushed
his wife of 30 years down the stairs?

09:16.640 --> 09:18.200
The woman that he loved...

09:21.520 --> 09:22.560
That he still loves.

09:25.880 --> 09:28.040
It's just not real, Jo.

10:10.040 --> 10:12.200
Thank you for coming in,
Mrs. Harding.

10:12.280 --> 10:17.120
Your father went walkabout
last night, and he had a fall.

10:17.200 --> 10:19.680
