39:43.840 --> 39:46.160
<i>You know what happens
when things get buried.</i>

39:46.800 --> 39:50.480
<i>Come on, your father used a fucking
fairy-tale to excuse his behaviour.</i>

39:50.560 --> 39:51.760
I'm sorry.

39:53.800 --> 39:56.520
Oh, God. I'm so sorry.

39:56.600 --> 39:57.880
This is my fault.

40:00.400 --> 40:02.840
This is all my fault.

40:02.920 --> 40:04.640
This is my fault.

40:15.240 --> 40:18.680
<i>- I was grieving!
- You were being selfish!</i>

40:19.600 --> 40:21.440
Lose a baby, get another one.

40:22.280 --> 40:23.800
You know what?

40:23.880 --> 40:26.800
If you're having a boy,
you should call him Lucas.

41:14.720 --> 41:16.360
You let me go.

41:20.520 --> 41:22.160
You let go of me.

41:29.280 --> 41:31.000
Jo, I did a bad thing.

41:31.080 --> 41:34.680
I did a really bad thing,
but I'm not a bad person.

41:37.200 --> 41:39.560
Bad things, Rob?

41:41.680 --> 41:44.120
How many bad things
do you have to do

41:44.200 --> 41:46.880
